# Phase 2 Walkthrough — LangGraph Agent

## What Was Built

Complete LangGraph agent for Cravely — a stateful 4-node graph that processes every user query:

```
user_message → [intent_classifier] → [query_builder] → [executor] → [response_formatter] → final_response
                     ↓ (chitchat/unclear)                                    ↑
                     └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

