## To Fully Test With Live API

Create `apps/api/.env` with real credentials:
```
SUPABASE_DATABASE_URL=postgresql://...
GOOGLE_GEMINI_API_KEY=...
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=...
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=...
```

Then run: `venv\Scripts\uvicorn.exe main:app --reload`
